    "description": "The beamZ Nereid120 is a powerful LED beam moving head for indoor and outdoor use. Equipped with a very powerful 120W LED source, enough to light up even the biggest dance floors. With an ultra-sharp 1.6° beam angle and an enchanting gobo wheel, prepare to be captivated by mesmerizing overlay effects. The motorized focus and the rotating prism (8+16 facets) split the beam to cover a larger area on any dance floor or stage. Very suitable for indoor and outdoor productions, events and installations that require a greater light output.",
